'''Tendrando Arms''' was the corporation founded by [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] and his wife, [[Tendra Risant Calrissian]] to produce modern [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droids]] during the war with the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Their first and stunningly successful product was the fearsome [[YVH 1]] [[Droid/Legends|droid]]. A later, less frightening, but by no means less deadly version called [[Nanna]] was used by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] as a nanny/bodyguard for his son, [[Ben Skywalker]].

Tendrando Arms continued as a defense contractor for the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] beyond the conclusion of the war.

